Oslo hotel and airport transfer details Cc As requested here are the details of the hotel nearest the Oslo Enron office it is a to minute walk away Scandic Hotel Sjlyst Sjlyst plass PO box Skyen phone Oslo Norway Fax The best way to get there from the airport is to use the Airport Express rail service and to SKOYEN It goes every minutes and takes about minutes You can get tickets at the airport and everyone speaks English Any questions please ask James as I am on maternity leave from tomorrow Thanks Teresa
